---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Layout title="Reading — June Kim" favicon="📚">
  <main>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Reading</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">Textbooks and papers, translated into runnable code with diagrams.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Foundations</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-3 text-gray-400">📚</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-3 text-gray-400">Subject</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-3 text-gray-400">Source</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 text-gray-400">License</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">∞</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/analysis/">Real Analysis</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Jiří Lebl</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🐱</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/category-theory/">Category Theory</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Bartosz Milewski</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🎲</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/game-theory/">Game Theory</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Jennifer Nordstrom</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🎰</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/probability/">Probability</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Grinstead &amp; Snell</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">GFDL</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">📡</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/info-theory/">Information Theory</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Shannon 1948 + Wikipedia</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">Public domain + CC BY-SA</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🪄</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/programming/">Programming</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Abelson &amp; Sussman (SICP) + DeNero</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0 + CC BY-SA 3.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🔢</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/discrete-math/">Discrete Math</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Oscar Levin</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">📐</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/linear-algebra/">Linear Algebra</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Jim Hefferon</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">GFDL + CC BY-SA 2.5</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🔗</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/algebra/">Abstract Algebra</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Tom Judson</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">GFDL</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🧠</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/cogsci/">Cognitive Science</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Lovelace textbook</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">📊</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/statistics/">Statistics</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">OpenIntro</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 3.0</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">∫</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/calculus/">Calculus</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Active Calculus</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">⚛</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/physics/">Physics</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Benjamin Crowell</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 3.0</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Papers</h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
      <table class="w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-3 text-gray-400">📚</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-3 text-gray-400">Collection</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 pr-3 text-gray-400">Description</th>
            <th class="text-left py-2 text-gray-400">Papers</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">🍞</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/natural-breadcrumbs/">Natural Breadcrumbs</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">Research papers decoded into runnable Python and SVG diagrams</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">21</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-2 pr-3">✏️</td>
            <td class="pr-3"><a href="/reading/lean/">Lean Proofs</a></td>
            <td class="pr-3 text-gray-400">The Natural Framework proof, file by file &mdash; plain English + Lean 4</td>
            <td class="text-gray-400">25</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-zinc-700 my-8"/>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Further reading (external)</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Permissive-licensed sources worth reading directly. Pointers, not derivatives.</p>
    <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-1 mb-4">
      <li><a href="https://forallx.openlogicproject.org/">forall x: Calgary</a> — propositional and predicate logic (CC BY 4.0)</li>
      <li><a href="https://openlogicproject.org/">Open Logic Project</a> — formal proof systems, model theory (CC BY 4.0)</li>
      <li><a href="https://leanprover-community.github.io/logic_and_proof/">Logic and Proof</a> — induction, Lean-flavored proofs (Apache 2.0)</li>
      <li><a href="https://softwarefoundations.cis.upenn.edu/plf-current/index.html">Software Foundations vol. 2</a> — Hoare logic, weakest preconditions (MIT)</li>
    </ul>

    <hr class="border-zinc-700 my-8"/>

    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4"><a href="https://june.kim/books/">My book notes</a> — 52 posts, 2012-2023.</p>

    <hr class="border-zinc-700 my-8"/>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs">This site is licensed <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/" class="underline hover:text-gray-400">CC BY-SA 4.0</a>. Fork it, build on it, keep it open.</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-1"><a href="https://june.kim" class="underline hover:text-gray-400">june.kim</a></p>

  </main>
</Layout>
